description:
Today on the show we had Rick Ross call in where he spoke about Big Boss Tips, Finding A Good Woman, Drake & Kanye Beef, his new book and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Texas Gov. Greg Abbott for signing a controversial election Integrity Bill and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
